authors:
  - family-names: "saner-spec"
    given-names: "saner-spec"
    orcid: ""
abstract: "AI-guided protein mutation design tool. Load a PDB structure, click a residue, and ESM-2 scores all 20 amino acid substitutions. Built-in AI tutor (DeepSeek v4-pro) explains mutation effects. Features 3Dmol.js viewer, batch surface scanning with heatmaps, DSSP/Ramachandran analysis, multi-PDB comparison, experimental protocol generation, primer design, and ESM validation against ProTherm benchmarks."
keywords:
  - "protein design"
  - "protein engineering"
  - "mutation analysis"
  - "ESM-2"
  - "bioinformatics"
  - "PDB"
  - "structural biology"
  - "ΔΔG prediction"
license: MIT
